canada februari consum price up 0.4 pct the canadian consum price index rose 0.4 pct in februari , to 135.8 , base 1981 , compar with a 0.2 pct rise in januari and a 0.4 pct rise in februari last year , statist canada said . the februari year-on year rise wa 4.0 pct compar with a 3.9 pct rise in january.r